  "detailed_description": "Animaddicts 2 is a Beat Em Up Game based on the 80s Cartoon for 1-4 players.<br><br>If you remembered watching the 80's cartoon series and had fond childhood memories of it, you’re going to appreciate this side-scrolling Beat Em Up game. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904320/extras/88a74f564b257ad8ca83c4eb43c0f9a0.poster.avif?t=1647068934\" width=680 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904320/extras/88a74f564b257ad8ca83c4eb43c0f9a0.webm?t=1647068934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904320/extras/88a74f564b257ad8ca83c4eb43c0f9a0.mp4?t=1647068934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can love how the visuals or animations remain true to the old cartoon series, cheesy, but goooood, just the way its meant to be <br><br>The Filmation cartoons, because of their constant use of animation, kind of looked like a videogame in many occasions. So we was thinking of how cool it would be to see a  game with old cartoon graphics.<br><br><strong>Features and Content</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> One Character to choose and play<br></li><li> Levels with different themes and enemies</li></ul><br><br><strong>Controller Support</strong><br>This game has Full Controller Support.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904320/extras/12e59182780d02a9957260ea01f46bef.avif?t=1647068934\" width=600 height=170 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Animaddicts 2 is a Beat Em Up Game based on the 80s Cartoon for 1-4 players.<br><br>If you remembered watching the 80's cartoon series and had fond childhood memories of it, you’re going to appreciate this side-scrolling Beat Em Up game. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904320/extras/88a74f564b257ad8ca83c4eb43c0f9a0.poster.avif?t=1647068934\" width=680 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904320/extras/88a74f564b257ad8ca83c4eb43c0f9a0.webm?t=1647068934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904320/extras/88a74f564b257ad8ca83c4eb43c0f9a0.mp4?t=1647068934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can love how the visuals or animations remain true to the old cartoon series, cheesy, but goooood, just the way its meant to be <br><br>The Filmation cartoons, because of their constant use of animation, kind of looked like a videogame in many occasions. So we was thinking of how cool it would be to see a  game with old cartoon graphics.<br><br><strong>Features and Content</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> One Character to choose and play<br></li><li> Levels with different themes and enemies</li></ul><br><br><strong>Controller Support</strong><br>This game has Full Controller Support.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904320/extras/12e59182780d02a9957260ea01f46bef.avif?t=1647068934\" width=600 height=170 /></span>",
